## Sunny orchestration

- Tell every Task agent: **query graphify first**, read files surgically, and (if it changed code) **`graphify update <project-root>` before returning**.
- After every code-changing agent, confirm the graph was refreshed (Maya tracks `graphUpdatedAt` in `state.json`); if it was skipped, run `graphify update <project-root>` before launching the next agent so it never inherits a stale graph.
- On intake, bootstrap once with `graphify .` if `graphify-out/` is missing; thereafter only `graphify update` between stages.

